subject: JUNit4: weird CVS issues
msgSnippet: Eclipse is giving me error messages like: Skipping builder com.agitator.eclipse.project.agitatorbuilder for project junit. Either the builder is missing from
messageBody:
Eclipse is giving me error messages like:

Skipping builder com.agitator.eclipse.project.agitatorbuilder for
project junit. Either the builder is missing from the install, or it
belongs to a project nature that is missing or disabled.

on the JUnit4 project. I'm guessing Kent's Eclipse settings include some
Agitar plugins most of us don't have. Is it possible for these to be
removed from CVS?
